00:43:25,119 --> 00:43:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam šta je to bilo.

1278
00:43:26,179 --> 00:43:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] I on kaže,

1279
00:43:27,679 --> 00:43:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi moji mogu povjerovat da Bog postoji.

1280
00:43:33,500 --> 00:43:36,800
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu povjerovat da je uskrsnuo.

1281
00:43:37,639 --> 00:43:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu povjerovat da me spasio.

1282
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu povjerovat da je došao na svijet.

1283
00:43:42,719 --> 00:43:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jednu stvar još uvijek ne mogu povjerovat,

1284
00:43:45,780 --> 00:43:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] kaže.

1285
00:43:46,119 --> 00:43:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da ću jednog dana ja,

1286
00:43:48,480 --> 00:43:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] ovako bijedan i grešan,

1287
00:43:50,940 --> 00:43:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] biti kao Isus.

1288
00:43:53,039 --> 00:43:56,860
[SPEAKER_00] Jednog dana ja ću biti kao Isus.

1289
00:43:56,860 --> 00:43:58,780
[SPEAKER_00] On ne može vjerovat

1290
00:43:58,780 --> 00:44:00,780
[SPEAKER_00] da je ljubav Bože toliko velika

1291
00:44:00,780 --> 00:44:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] da pređe tolki jaz

1292
00:44:02,920 --> 00:44:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] između

1293
00:44:03,460 --> 00:44:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] mojeg stanja

1294
00:44:04,599 --> 00:44:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo gdje je Isus.

1295
00:44:07,639 --> 00:44:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] I pozvao se na Ivanovu poslanicu

1296
00:44:10,820 --> 00:44:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] koja kaže da ćemo biti jednaki.

1297
00:44:12,619 --> 00:44:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] Da ćemo biti nalik Bogu

1298
00:44:17,219 --> 00:44:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] jednog dana.

1299
00:44:18,619 --> 00:44:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] I on kaže,

1300
00:44:20,719 --> 00:44:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] ja mogu samo zahvaliti.

1301
00:44:22,940 --> 00:44:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] I krene moliti u jezicima.

1302
00:44:25,400 --> 00:44:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, da.

1303
00:44:26,380 --> 00:44:28,320
[SPEAKER_00] I spusti se pomazanje.

1304
00:44:28,320 --> 00:44:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] Spusti se strah.

1305
00:44:31,500 --> 00:44:33,219
[SPEAKER_00] Strah opoštovanje.

1306
00:44:33,219 --> 00:44:35,800
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je izrekao svoju zahvalu.

1307
00:44:35,800 --> 00:44:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo gotovi bili.

1308
00:44:37,440 --> 00:44:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] suze, jer ona je.

1309
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ne zna šta bi od sebe.

1310
00:44:40,099 --> 00:44:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] E to je mistika.

1311
00:44:42,619 --> 00:44:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ko nas Bog želi pozvati.

1312
00:44:45,300 --> 00:44:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] A Papa Franjo kaže jednu stvar

1313
00:44:49,039 --> 00:44:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] ne smijemo izgubiti.

1314
00:44:54,619 --> 00:44:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] posebno mi mladi.

1315
00:44:55,519 --> 00:44:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ne smijemo izgubiti,

1316
00:44:57,639 --> 00:44:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao kaže Papa Franjo,

1317
00:44:59,420 --> 00:45:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] oduševljenost i radost.

1318
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] i to mena dodaje smisla za humor.

1319
00:45:13,500 --> 00:45:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] To nama treba.

1320
00:45:14,500 --> 00:45:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] To nama treba.

1321
00:45:14,800 --> 00:45:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tad naše nošenje križa je podnošljivo.

1322
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] Tad imamo perspektivu.

1323
00:45:22,539 --> 00:45:24,179
[SPEAKER_00] Tad nam Bog otvara.

1324
00:45:24,179 --> 00:45:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ko što otvara ovoj zajednici.

1325
00:45:25,760 --> 00:45:27,219
[SPEAKER_00] I vjerujem da će otvarati,

1326
00:45:27,219 --> 00:45:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] tako se odazovemo.

1327
00:45:28,360 --> 00:45:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] i zato vas pozivam ovo ljeto.

1328
00:45:30,019 --> 00:45:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] Odazovite se ovim pozivima.

1329
00:45:32,579 --> 00:45:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pripremite svoje srce,

1330
00:45:34,760 --> 00:45:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer Bog želi s vama nešto učiniti.

1331
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] Želi vas podignuti stepenicu iznad.

1332
00:45:40,539 --> 00:45:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] Želi vam dati možda službu,

1333
00:45:42,840 --> 00:45:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] možda neki novi odnos prijateljstva.

1334
00:45:44,940 --> 00:45:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko se toga samo u ovoj godini dogodilo.

1335
00:45:47,699 --> 00:45:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo bebače.

1336
00:45:49,659 --> 00:45:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo nove bračne parove.

1337
00:45:52,980 --> 00:45:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] I zaručnike.

1338
00:45:58,360 --> 00:46:00,219
[SPEAKER_00] Bog će davati.

1339
00:46:00,219 --> 00:46:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] I ne moramo se bojati.

1340
00:46:02,019 --> 00:46:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] On ima plan.

1341
00:46:04,099 --> 00:46:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] A mi ostanimo radosni i u nadi.

1342
00:46:06,739 --> 00:46:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Papa Franjom da 40 godina

1343
00:46:09,239 --> 00:46:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] moli ovu molitvu koja je meni jako dobra bila.

1344
00:46:11,800 --> 00:46:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ću vam pročitati.

1345
00:46:13,940 --> 00:46:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] To je napisao Thomas More

1346
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji imao vrlo mnogo smisla za humor.

1347
00:46:20,199 --> 00:46:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] On napisao ovako.

1348
00:46:21,400 --> 00:46:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi gospodine dobru probavu,

1349
00:46:23,920 --> 00:46:26,239
[SPEAKER_00] a i nešto za probavljanje.

1350
00:46:27,239 --> 00:46:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi tjelesno zdravlje

1351
00:46:28,480 --> 00:46:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] s dobrim raspoloženjem potrebnim da ga čuvam.

1352
00:46:31,099 --> 00:46:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi gospodine svetu dušu

1353
00:46:33,599 --> 00:46:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] koje će blago biti ono što je dobro i čisto,

1354
00:46:36,380 --> 00:46:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne preplaši grijeha,

1355
00:46:38,260 --> 00:46:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego nek u tvojoj prisutnosti nađe način

1356
00:46:40,880 --> 00:46:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] da stvari ponovno dovede u red.

1357
00:46:42,539 --> 00:46:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi dušu koja ne zna za dosadu,

1358
00:46:45,780 --> 00:46:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] mrmljanja, uzdisanja, ni jadikovke.

1359
00:46:48,760 --> 00:46:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] I ne dopusti da se pretjerano mučim

1360
00:46:51,539 --> 00:46:54,760
[SPEAKER_00] radi onog previše nametljivog što se zove ja.

1361
00:46:55,800 --> 00:46:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi gospodine smisao za humor,

1362
00:46:57,980 --> 00:47:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] udjeli mi milost razumijevanja šale,

1363
00:47:00,619 --> 00:47:03,280
[SPEAKER_00] da u životu upoznam malo radosti

1364
00:47:03,280 --> 00:47:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] i da je podijelim s drugima.

1365
00:47:04,940 --> 00:47:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] Tako neka bude.

1366
00:47:06,539 --> 00:47:07,860
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

